ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Regarding this post, it is worth reading again the comments in ProMED-mail post 20140704.2588229.

To date, China has reported 2 events of FMD serotype A; these events were associated with 17 outbreaks.
1. Event start date of 9 Jun 2013, last follow-up report No .12, 1 Apr 2015, a total of 9 outbreaks.
http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/temp/reports/en_fup_0000017422_20150401_122457.pdf
2. Event start date of 12 Apr 2013, last follow-up report No. 12, 1 Apr 2015, a total of 8 outbreaks. http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/temp/reports/en_fup_0000017420_20150401_123001.pdf. - Mod.CRD

